name: Jailbreak (itch) (Carattiniw)
description:
Escape your cell and find the key, this will be your only ticket to freedom, don't get caught! 

This mini-game was made in collaboration with a team of students from the University of Central Florida.

Controls

-WASD and mouse

-Gamepad controller

Interact

-E or X button on Xbox Controller

Jailbreak Team Members 

William Carattini (Team Lead, Programmer)

Jason Johnson (3D Artist)

Marco Peralta (3D Artist)

Ashley Prieto (3D Artist/Animations)

Matthew Wisner (Programmer)
